@page "/blogbuilder"

<div class="alert alert-warning" role="alert">
    <h4 class="alert-heading">Blog Builder Retired</h4>
    <p>
        The WYSIWYG block-builder (<code>OptAPostBuilder</code>) is no longer the recommended authoring path
        and has been removed from this playground.
    </p>
    <p>
        Author blog posts and documentation pages in <strong>Markdown</strong> using
        <code>OptionA.Blazor.Blog</code> (<code>OptADocument</code>), and use
        <code>OptionA.Blazor.Playground</code> for interactive component previews.
    </p>
</div>